        <div class="body">
            <p>This is undocumented, but the expected behaviour when a translation object is set in the element.</p>

<p>A new feature allows you to ignore the value posted, which will prevent the value from being set in the object. Simply call:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$element-&gt;setIgnore(true);
</code></pre>

<p>and this will prevent submissions from overwriting the value.</p>

